title: Road blocked after car transporter crash
text:
The car transporter left the road. Credit: ITV Border The A689 road outside Carlisle Airport has been partially blocked after an accident involving a car transporter that left the road.
The vehicle, which was carrying a number of cars, left the road at around 10am this morning.
Police are directing traffic at the scene, and the road has been blocked between the airport turn off and Ruleholme turn off.
